04:13.042 --> 04:15.576
"One part bee pollen,
honey, and some... "

04:15.611 --> 04:18.440
- Oliver! This has your name on it.
- Oh.

04:19.982 --> 04:21.118
Huh...

04:24.187 --> 04:25.988
Well, hello there.

04:28.057 --> 04:30.524
"Oliver, this found its way to my inbox,

04:30.560 --> 04:32.697
"obviously intended for the DLO.

04:32.722 --> 04:35.790
"Check out the postmark
and return address.

04:35.815 --> 04:37.815
"Can't wait to hear
the story behind this.

04:38.167 --> 04:40.835
Speaking of which, I hope
your date on Saturday goes... "

04:40.955 --> 04:43.052
_

